# Bundled mpv sidecar binary (Phase 3 P1). ~4.5MB+, fetched/built in CI rather
# than committed. CI must run `brew install mpv` (or build mpv) and copy the
# binary to src-tauri/binaries/mpv-<target-triple> (e.g.
# mpv-aarch64-apple-darwin) before `tauri build`; see src-tauri/src/player.rs.
# NOTE: the brew mpv links Homebrew dylibs under /opt/homebrew/opt/** — for a
# distributable bundle those must also be relocated/bundled (e.g. dylibbundler).
src-tauri/binaries/
